# rates-provider

Python project with source code in `src/` and tests in `tests/`.

## Run

```bash
pip install -e .
python3 -m rates_provider
# or via console script:
rates-provider
```

## Checks

```bash
python3 -m pytest tests/ -v
ruff check .
mypy .
```
